WEBVTT

NOTE
Tire Fire Simulation — AF31 Suppression Demonstration
Duration: ~1 minute 46 seconds

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.000
[A car tire placed on a testing surface — firefighter approaches with a 1300°C blowtorch]

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:28.000
[Blowtorch applied to the tire — it ignites and begins to burn intensely]

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:45.000
[On-screen text: "Thick Black Smoke" — dense black smoke billows from the burning tire]

00:00:45.000 --> 00:01:05.000
[Second firefighter applies AF31 water-based solution via portable extinguisher directly onto the burning tire]

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:25.000
[Flames extinguished completely — no re-ignition after AF31 application]

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:46.000
[On-screen text: "Eco-Friendly · Water Based · Unlimited Utility" — AF31 effective on all fire types including rubber and petroleum-based fires]
